channel.title: Fly - Winter J. Studios
channel.description:
Woah... it’s been a very long time since I’ve posted. Huh... well I got a very awesome new track right now! Go check it out! Please give feedback if you’d like to see what I should improve on or just a complement in general!
Also I’ve missed on a lot of things since last year. Just starting to use Auxy again.
Soundcloud: [Fly - Winter J. Studios](https://soundcloud.com/tropical_madman/fly-winter-j-studios)
I’m also changing my name soon so I’ll start using Winter J. Studios instead of what I have now.
Glad to be back! ^-^
